        <updateDate>2020-10-21T14:19:06Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>No Pay for Proxy Voting Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires that one day's pay be withheld from the compensation of a Representative and deposited into an escrow account for distribution on the last day of the Congress for each day that a Representative uses a designated proxy to cast a vote or record their presence in the House of Representatives. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
